Hi Bruce,



Nobody is ostracized here, I think you=92ve mistaken this gro=
up for some of
the others you=92ve participated in. That=92s part of

the r=
eason why we=92re here. This group is about trying different things.



Ye=
s, I hear your view on the easily recognizable names. There may be other
pe=
ople out there who agree with you, but that=92s as 

far as it goes. Can=92=
t change or influence someone else=92s opinion. Best we
can do is to focus =
on the positive fact that we=92re communicating

with spirit, regardless of=
 who it is.



Welcome to the group,

Keith









