Theory of evp

These are my thoughts on why we get cl=
ass A or class B or lower, why 
some evps stand on their own and some have =
to be edited by an audio 
editing program to be heard. I am sure that all s=
erious evp 
researchers do recording sessions in their homes more than anyw=
here 
else such as on a field investigation. If your like me you do a 
reco=
rding just about everyday. In my experience there are many 
different types=
 of evp researchers you have your die hard white noise 
users, your silent =
no question no background noise individuals your 
only on investigations or=
 in ascertain room of the house people and 
the radicals that reach out for=
 new methods and ideas and are always 
experimenting with different ways to=
 record evp and dedicating a lot 
of brain power to try and come up with a =
way to make the break 
through to real time communication as apposed to rec=
ording a question 
and answer session to be analyzed later.
Then you have t=
he researchers like me that embrace with an open mind 
all forms of evp as =
well as itc and any other form of paranormal 
research and investigation, s=
ee I am the type of PI that will try new 
methods and post them to a forum =
or on my website so that others may 
see what I am working on and maybe giv=
e it a try themselves and 
hopefully further the method and the knowledge o=
f it. Only to come 
under fire from the so called sceptics that believe the=
y must at any 
cost negatively view any presented outcome to give themselve=
s 
credibility. 
Anyway this is turning into a rant and getting away from t=
he subject. 
Many evp researchers if not all that I see and read and have c=
ontact 
with are under the assumption that, and don&#39;t get me wrong they may=

be 100% correct that all evp are formed the same way with the spirit 
usi=
ng whatever form of ambient energy is available to form a message 
whether =
it be artificially supplied by the researcher or natural such 
as emf energ=
y.
I do subscribe to this theory that spirits do need some sort of 
energy =
to form words and place them onto our recording medium, that 
is not my dis=
pute.
I also believe that the majority of researchers believe an evp is an =

evp and the only valid evp is the one that can be heard loudly and 
clearl=
y from the raw recording, I do not believe in this ideology. I 
believe the=
re are two distinct and different ways we receive evp one 
from the physica=
l plane and one from the spiritual plane. I believe 
that the only way to r=
eceive what has been classified as a class A 
evp is from an earthbound or =
grounded spirit that is actually 
haunting a location and is capable of uti=
lizing the energy in the 
location much more efficiently for the reason tha=
t the spirit is 
among the investigator and can take advantage of the close=
 proximity 
to the recording device and feed off of the physical and ambien=
t 
energy supplied by the individual or individuals in the recording 
area.=
 I also suspect that at times if we are lucky enough to be doing 
a recordi=
ng at the right time we can record a class A evp from a 
spirit that is not=
 grounded but in visitation at that time.
But the class A & B++ evps must b=
e obtained from a spirit that is 
occupying the same area as the recording =
device.
the second type of evp is the spiritual plane evp, messages recorde=
d 
from spirits that have crossed over and are in the spiritual world, I 
b=
elieve they are still capable of sending evp messages from the 
spirit worl=
d only they must also use the ambient energy surrounding 
the recorder or c=
ompile it and place it onto the recorder. In other 
words a much harder and=
 less effective method for the spirit leaving 
the message. Therefore the m=
essages we receive in this manner are 
often weak quiet and a bit distorted=
 but they are there.
If we take the time to look for them and clean them up=
 most of them 
are understandable also the majority of these messages tend =
to be of 
a personal nature most likely from friends or loved ones that hav=
e 
crossed. The only thing that stops these messages from being 
discovered=
 is that almost all the paranormal community subscribes to 
the idea that t=
he only valid evp is the class A evp that does not 
need to be cleaned or e=
nhanced in any way.
There are many evp researchers out there I&#39;m sure that =
have started 
and adhered to the method of evp capture that they first lear=
ned 
about in a book or on the Internet and have not for lack of 
informati=
on or the opportunity to learn how to edit a recording using 
an audio edit=
ing program stuck to the strict set of recording 
techniques that are mostl=
y explained on the net in one form or 
another. And I also believe that the=
y witness the systematic 
slaughter of anyone who dares to post or mention =
any new or radical 
idea or form of evp capture so they shy away from takin=
g the leap and 
trying some new or seldom recognized method and stick to th=
e &quot;OLD&quot; 
and most widely accepted method out of fear of being ostracised 
a=
mo9ng their paranormal peers and I do mean peers , No one in this 
field is=
 any better than the next person there are only PI&#39;s with 
more experience =
and ones with less but some with the more experience 
go through the motion=
s of investigation with blinders on following an 
antiquated set of investi=
gatory and research rules and not opening 
their minds to anything else.
My=
 theory of the two different types of evp is formed from my 
personal exper=
ience with different methods of recording and capture 
and I have evps that=
 are very personal in nature mentioning my name 
as well as subject matter =
unique to me and my family that would have 
been totally over looked if not=
 for a good editing session.
NO one can make me believe especially the so c=
alled seasoned veterans 
that an evp that mentions my name and that of frie=
nds and or loved 
ones can be randomly put together from editing filters be=
ing used on 
raw static.
Well those are my thought on evp please do not hes=
itate to let me 
know what you think of this theory.
Bruce halliday




